{
  "stem": "3659.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I'm clean.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I-- I wash.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I bathe every day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I'm not dirty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You're nothing but a dirty Jew, and you should die like a dog.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And very shortly after, about a month after, I was on the street, and I saw SS men walking with doberman pinscher dogs, and they had two on each-- each side.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were-- they were holding the reins of the dogs and these black-- big, black dogs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I saw a truck at the end of the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there was a plank that was lined up on the back end of the truck, and I saw they were herding people into the truck.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And at that moment, all of a sudden, I said, oh, my god, these are Jewish people that I knew from the neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And one man couldn't run as fast as they wanted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So this SS guy let go of the dogs, and he sicced them on the people there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And as a child, when I saw how those dogs attacked a human being, this never went out of my mind.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "To this day, I will never enter a home if there's a doberman dog in that house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I will never have-- if I see a doberman on the street, I will run on the other side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It is something that you can never, ever forget, that vision of those dogs attacking the people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "This is-- this is bad for me at this moment, because I see the picture in front of me again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All I saw was ripping, ripping.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I just went-- I ran.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
